Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:03.78,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}向着未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:05.95,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}开始前行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.45,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}无谋的挑战者啊
